    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "¿Cómo varía la tarifa por milla en función de la distancia total del viaje?\n",
        "¿Son los viajes cortos proporcionalmente más caros que los viajes largos?"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "IZqFn7RT5-Us"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "rides_c = rides.dropna(subset=['price'])"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Etlv0joo0pOm"
      },
      "execution_count": 20,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "rides_c = rides_c[rides_c['distance'] > 0]"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "ZgfFG4t30uk-"
      },
      "execution_count": 21,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "rides_c['price_per_mile'] = rides_c['price'] / rides_c['distance']"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Q9cJeEWu0wSs"
      },
      "execution_count": 22,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
